OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FIreland is significantly behind its
OL,7,Ftargets for installing heat pumps and
OL,8,Fthe deep retrofitting of homes,
OL,9,Faccording to analysis by a think tank.
OL,11,FThe Economic and Social Research
OL,12,FInstitute (ESRI) said that projections
OL,13,Findicated that targets for retrofitted
OL,14,Fproperties were unlikely to be met and
OL,15,Fthat policies might be needed to boost
OL,16,Fthe number of energy-efficient homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
