CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FIreland has committed to reduce its
OL,7,Fgreenhouse gas emissions, as measured
OL,8,Fin 2018, by 51% by 2030, but
OL,9,Fenvironment minister Darragh O'Brien
OL,10,Fhas acknowledged it will achieve only
OL,11,Fhalf of this target.
OL,13,FThe Environmental Protection Agency
OL,14,Fhas projected that Ireland will reduce
OL,15,Fits emissions by 23% by 2030, assuming
OL,16,Fit implements in full its current
OL,17,Fplans and policies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FThe Government's Climate Action Plan
OL,7,F2025 sets a target to install 400,000
OL,8,Fheat pumps in existing homes and
OL,9,F200,000 heat pumps in new dwellings;
OL,10,Fand to upgrade 500,000 homes to a
OL,11,FBuilding Energy Rating (BER) of B2 or
OL,12,Fhigher.
OL,14,FDeep retrofits, deemed as bringing a
OL,15,Fhome to an energy rating of B2 or
OL,16,Fhigher, had reached 11.5%, or 57,932,
OL,17,Fof the 2030 targets by the end of 2024.
OL,19,FAnd there have been 14,194, heat pump
OL,20,Finstallations, which is 3.5% of the
OL,21,F2030 target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,F"We find that progress is lagging
OL,7,Fconsiderably behind that required to
OL,8,Fachieve the stated targets," the
OL,9,Freport said.
OL,11,F"Assuming this same acceleration is
OL,12,Fmaintained every year until 2030,
OL,13,Ftotal deep retrofits by 2030 are
OL,14,Fprojected to reach nearly 334,000, or
OL,15,F66.7% of the target, while total heat
OL,16,Fpump installations are projected to
OL,17,Freach nearly 51,400, or 12.9% of the
OL,18,Ftarget."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]sD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FThe analysis said barriers to
OL,7,Fimplementation included high capital
OL,8,Fcosts and disruption, with more than
OL,9,F40% of homeowners saying they had no
OL,10,Finterest in changing their home's
OL,11,Fproperties or layout.
OL,13,FThe report said the median cost of a
OL,14,Fdeep energy retrofit ranged from
OL,15,F22,914 euro for an apartment to 66,503
OL,16,Feuro for a detached house, with the
OL,17,Fportion of the cost covered by the
OL,18,Fhomeowner ranging from 16,378 to
OL,19,F42,900 euro.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FIn the rental market, the cost of deep
OL,7,Fretrofitting a rental property from a
OL,8,FC rating was 30,000 euro, while a deep
OL,9,Fretrofit from a G rating was 43,000
OL,10,Feuro.
OL,12,FThe report said that the rental market
OL,13,Fsuffered from the "split incentives"
OL,14,Fproblem: a resident homeowner benefits
OL,15,Ffrom reduced bills and an increase in
OL,16,Fproperty value after an energy
OL,17,Fretrofit; but a tenant benefits only
OL,18,Ffrom the former and in most
OL,19,Fcircumstances, the landlord only
OL,20,Fbenefits from the latter.
OL,26,@uD@SOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FThe ESRI also said research and
OL,7,Fanalysis indicated BER ratings could
OL,8,F"deviate considerably from actual
OL,9,Fconsumption" as they were based on
OL,10,Fpredicted rather than actual energy
OL,11,Fuse.
OL,13,FIt also cited an Irish study that
OL,14,Ffound households consumed around
OL,15,F10,869kWh/year, and that this "does
OL,16,Fnot vary considerably" whether it is
OL,17,Fan A-rated house or a G-rated house.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@LO]wD@_OUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,F"In an Irish context, (Coyne and Denny
OL,7,F2021) find that theoretical energy use
OL,8,Fis, on average, 17% below actual
OL,9,Fenergy use, and this difference varies
OL,10,Fby the BER rating of the dwelling,"
OL,11,Fthe ESRI said.
OL,13,F"These findings correspond to those of
OL,14,F(Meles et al 2023; 2024), where BER is
OL,15,Fshown to have a lesser than expected
OL,16,Fpredictive power on energy consumption
OL,17,Fand heat loss."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]uD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,FThe research said policy changes could
OL,7,Fbe considered to address the shortfall
OL,8,Fin heat pump and retrofit targets,
OL,9,Fincluding a switch to lower-cost
OL,10,Fcarbon fuel, making retrofit schemes
OL,11,Fand loans more accessible to lower-
OL,12,Fincome families, and more flexible
OL,13,Fenergy options such as heat storage.
OL,15,FDr Muireann Lynch, senior research
OL,16,Fofficer at the ESRI, said: "This
OL,17,Freview synthesises the empirical
OL,18,Fevidence on residential heat
OL,19,Fdecarbonisation progress and
OL,20,Fchallenges in Ireland.
OL,26,@xD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,F"It highlights substantial shortfalls
OL,7,Fin delivery and discrepancies in
OL,8,Fperformance metrics to date.
OL,10,F"In this context, additional policy
OL,11,Fmeasures may warrant consideration."
OL,13,FDr Niall Farrell, associate research
OL,14,Fprofessor at the ESRI, said: "The
OL,15,Fstudy examines barriers to retrofit
OL,16,Fuptake and tracks progress in
OL,17,Fdeployment.
OL,19,F"Projected trends point to a likely
OL,20,Fshortfall in emissions savings
OL,21,Frelative to climate objectives.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@dO]vD@^OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773111798
OL,3,CIreland 'lagging considerably' behind
OL,4,Ctargets for heat pumps and retrofits
OL,6,F"Drawing on multiple data sources and
OL,7,Frecent studies, the analysis
OL,8,Fhighlights key evidence gaps that are
OL,9,Fcrucial for tracking real-world
OL,10,Foutcomes against climate targets."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
